    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0789a05"/><head><date from-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322132856" to-iso="+1127-06-18"><anchor xml:id="beg0789001"/>宋<anchor xml:id="end0789001"/></date><placeName key="PL000000018855"><placeName>廬山</placeName><placeName>圓通院</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010755">緣德</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0789a06"/><persName key="A010755">釋緣德</persName>，俗姓<name>黃</name>，<placeName key="PL000000011520">錢塘</placeName>人也。父<persName key="A010756">超</persName>修學儒術，而<lb
ed="T" n="0789a07"/>長於繢畫，傳<persName key="A010757">周昉</persName>佛粉本，受筆法於<placeName key="PL000000013012">吳興</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0789a08"/><persName key="A010759">李沼</persName>長史。<persName key="A010755">德</persName>幼有出家之志，心性孤僻而寡<lb
ed="T" n="0789a09"/>合，遂往<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>受具<ptr target="#n826"/>，習禪法於<placeName key="PL000000011435">天龍寺</placeName><persName key="A010691">道怤<lb
ed="T" n="0789a10"/><roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>。尋往<placeName key="PL000000018571">江西</placeName>問道<ptr target="#n827"/>，自<placeName key="PL000000018911">雲居</placeName>往<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬阜</placeName>，孤<lb
ed="T" n="0789a11"/>節高岸，實不見有所欲<ptr target="#n829"/>。<placeName key="PL000000000122">江南國</placeName>主<persName key="A021837">李<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>召<lb
ed="T" n="0789a12"/>入內道場安置，慮其不群，別構<placeName key="PL000000057398">羅漢院</placeName>處<lb
ed="T" n="0789a13"/>之。苦求入山，請住<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬山</placeName>新院<ptr target="#n831"/>，乃列威儀導<lb
ed="T" n="0789a14"/>引焉。<persName key="A010755">德</persName>且裝衣荷擔而入，然後升座，對答參<lb
ed="T" n="0789a15"/>問焉。<ref type="person" target="#A021837">其國主</ref>賜賚，未嘗以表牋報謝。有國<lb
ed="T" n="0789a16"/>老<persName key="A004061">宋齊丘</persName>者，<anchor xml:id="beg0789sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0789sgsz1"/>以師道。以<date notBefore-iso="+0968-12-21" key="j20749702077860" notAfter-iso="+0976-11-19"><name>開寶</name>中</date>卒于山<lb
ed="T" n="0789a17"/>院<ptr target="#n407"/>。<persName key="A010755">德</persName>一生服用，熟韋袴襪而已。行杜多法，<lb
ed="T" n="0789a18"/>供億<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1227"/>諸禪侶，厨無匱乏。或謂<persName key="A010755">德</persName>有黃白術<lb
ed="T" n="0789a19"/>焉<ptr type="glossary" target="#g130"/>。</p>
